crawl (2:0.12.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release.
  * Revert -Os, benchmarks show it greatly reduces speed even on cache
    starved machines, and Crawl is too CPU hungry for small disk savings
    to matter.
  * Autodetect -fno-fat-lto-objects.

